1
00:00:03,392 --> 00:00:09,472
=Ex-boyfriend & Boss=

2
00:00:09,472 --> 00:00:10,970
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:11,359 --> 00:00:13,759
Mr. Liao, what do you need me for?

4
00:00:18,199 --> 00:00:18,839
Ms. Zhou,

5
00:00:18,920 --> 00:00:20,280
about the order you placed this time.

6
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:21,640
The quantity of the sleepers

7
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:22,640
is too large this time.

8
00:00:22,879 --> 00:00:24,440
Could it be 128?

9
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,160
Just make the delivery.

10
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:27,920
If someone has made the entry,
then let it be.

11
00:00:28,199 --> 00:00:30,519
What we need
is exactly 128 cubic meters.

12
00:00:31,239 --> 00:00:33,439
But 128 cubic meters is too much.

13
00:00:33,439 --> 00:00:34,439
You need it urgently.

14
00:00:34,439 --> 00:00:35,880
We don't have enough stock right now.

15
00:00:37,079 --> 00:00:39,640
If there's no stock,
use other stock to make up for it.

16
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:41,320
It can be replaced later on.

17
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:42,520
Mr. Liao,

18
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:43,280
this...

19
00:00:44,159 --> 00:00:45,600
This recording is forged.

20
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,359
It's her. It's Tong Nian.

21
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:50,600
It's Tong Nian together with
Zhang Qianyang slandering me.

22
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:55,159
Why are you all siding with her?

23
00:00:55,759 --> 00:00:58,240
It was her who told Hu
to not let me come to Changtian.

24
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,679
After joining the company,

25
00:00:59,679 --> 00:01:01,640
she went out of her way
to please various leaders.

26
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:04,760
Even Mr. Zhou
wants her to be his secretary.

27
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:08,000
Won't any of you say something?

28
00:01:09,319 --> 00:01:10,840
You're still being stubborn now.

29
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:13,799
I simply did my job well.

30
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:15,959
I didn't seek to please anyone.

31
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:26,560
I think I understand now.

32
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,239
You're all in this together.

33
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:32,120
I will lodge a complaint
that you are bullying people with power.

34
00:01:33,799 --> 00:01:34,640
Then go ahead.

35
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,439
So this photo

36
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,879
will also appear
in the company's chat group.

37
00:01:41,359 --> 00:01:43,319
Do you think
once your affair is exposed,

38
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:44,439
he will protect you?

39
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:49,840
Go ahead and send it.

40
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,680
Do you think he will let you off?

41
00:01:52,359 --> 00:01:53,920
So you think I would let him off?

42
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:01,280
Alright.

43
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:03,959
This doesn't affect the company much.

44
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:05,959
I've talked to Zhang Qianyang.

45
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:07,319
Retrieving the sleepers.

46
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,120
I will handle the rest.

47
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,639
Do not act rashly.

48
00:02:17,599 --> 00:02:19,400
Why is she like this?

49
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:24,039
It's her. She forced someone to resign.

50
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:24,919
It's her?

51
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:31,919
Nian.

52
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:33,280
What's wrong?

53
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,439
You haven't checked

54
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:35,759
the company's intranet?

55
00:02:36,159 --> 00:02:37,879
The intranet? No, I haven't.

56
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,439
Before Zhou Xinxin resigned,

57
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:41,680
she dropped a video screenshot
onto the company's intranet.

58
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,800
You go take a look now.

59
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,240
Go ahead.

60
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,319
Okay.

61
00:02:45,319 --> 00:02:46,000
I'll do it.

62
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,700
(Zhou Xinxin of After-sales Service
reports with real name.)

63
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:56,200
(Changtian Industry Chat Group)
(Intense internal competition at Changtian,)

64
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:58,000
(using support from leaders
in other departments,)

65
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,120
(seizing colleagues' resources
in the workplace,)

66
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,240
(leading in bullying employees,)

67
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,319
(and forcing them
to resign voluntarily.)

68
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:08,439
Okay, reversing black and white.

69
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,719
What are you thinking,
being so engrossed?

70
00:03:18,879 --> 00:03:19,800
Work-related matters.

71
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,319
Today's meeting ended early.

72
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,159
You don't have to go.

73
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:25,240
Alright.

74
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:27,400
Well, you saw...

75
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,240
The intranet? I've seen it.

76
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:31,280
Don't take it to heart.

77
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:33,879
As long as you don't take it to heart,

78
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,360
I won't take it to heart.

79
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,400
And don't you know me by now?

80
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,400
I'll forget about it quickly.

81
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:41,759
That's right.
Zhou Zhengyi is a company veteran.

82
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,919
He misuses his power
based on his achievements.

83
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,159
Zhao Qiqi and I are

84
00:03:45,180 --> 00:03:46,800
gathering evidence
of his illegal activities.

85
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,199
Then keep it up.

86
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:50,719
Let me know if you need my help.

87
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:55,199
Nian, don't worry.

88
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,319
I will certainly
make him face punishment.

89
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:00,560
Okay.

90
00:04:05,199 --> 00:04:06,240
Boss, we're in a meeting.

91
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,039
Where have you been?

92
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,840
How's Zhou Zhengyi's case progressing?

93
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:09,919
Almost there.

94
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,479
Just need the evidence of

95
00:04:11,479 --> 00:04:13,080
him colluding with
two suppliers privately.

96
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:15,400
Should I organize these pieces of

97
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,800
evidence and send them to the board now?

98
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:17,879
No need.

99
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:20,639
But regarding the issue of
his improper personal conduct,

100
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,600
it could actually
be sent to his families.

101
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:26,759
I heard Mrs. Zhou
is not someone to be trifled with.

102
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:28,600
Understood.

103
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,480
What's wrong, Sha?

104
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,319
Tong Nian, didn't I tell you
to stay away from him.

105
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,279
You believe me?

106
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,240
Sha, what's the matter?

107
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,360
Take your time.

108
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:45,920
Half a year ago,

109
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,639
I was in the Production Department.

110
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:53,959
He sent me harassing messages
every day under the pretext of work.

111
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,399
Later on,

112
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,439
he became even bolder

113
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:02,959
and started to physically harass me

114
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:04,639
on my way off work.

115
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:09,759
Do you have evidence?

116
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:11,839
I...

117
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:14,279
Sha,

118
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:18,199
next, I plan to
report Zhou Zhengyi by real name.

119
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,439
But my evidence might not be sufficient.

120
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,720
If you are willing to believe me,

121
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,120
I will redact
all your personal information.

122
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,839
Maybe it's worth a try.

123
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,720
Would you be willing to trust me?

124
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:38,399
I have chat records,

125
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,560
recorded phone calls,

126
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:41,720
and also evidence from
resigned colleagues too.

127
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,759
I'll give them all to you.

128
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:44,519
Okay.

129
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,279
Thank you.

130
00:05:52,826 --> 00:05:54,682
(Report Letter from Tong Nian)

131
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,680
Now Zhou is going to suffer a loss.

132
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:16,879
This matter won't cause him much loss.

133
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:18,800
We have to wait for
the board's conclusion.
